nodes.text: Garren trees grew on the Core World of Chandrila. The trees lined the walkway of Hanna City's Grand Promenade of the Rebellion. In 7 ABY, as the former rebel Lando Calrissian and the Free Ryloth Movement member Kaasha Bateen walked along the promenade, preepnobs hooted back and forth in the nearby garren trees.
The garren tree appeared in the 2018 novel Last Shot, written by Daniel José Older.
